-- N. Korea ‘Clear and Direct Threat’ to U.S., Locklear Says
-- B y   G o p a l   R a t n a m
-- 2013-04-08T18:16:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-08/n-korea-clear-and-direct-threat-to-u-s-locklear-says.html
North Korea ’s violations of United
Nations Security Council resolutions that prohibit building and
testing of nuclear weapons and long-range missiles are a threat
to the U.S., Admiral Samuel Locklear will tell Congress.  North Korea’s actions “represent a clear and direct threat
to U.S. national security and regional peace and stability,”
Locklear, head of the U.S. Pacific Command, said in testimony
prepared for a Senate Armed Services Committee hearing tomorrow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
